divs: Sighting DetailsAt home watching a clear evening sky around 8:40pm, noticed a few planes strobe in area then as I looked at a star in the southern sky a bright light materialized near the star only to slowly dematerialize. It repeated this 3 times within 2mins. then slowly disappeared.
